      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HOT SHOT ETHICS (1) is better than last start when seventh (30.58) from Box 1 at Wentworth Park over 520m. Reliable out of the boxes and should take advantage of the inside draw. Rates on top in this line up. ICEBERG AHEAD (7) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing second behind Mia Zipper (22.60) in a Grade 5. Has the pace to be prominent. Has good speed and can quickly clear the pack out wide. Expected to be in this for a long way. HOOKED ON JOY (8) turned in a better effort at Gosford last start, finishing third behind Imogene Pass (22.60) in a Grade 5. Stalked the pace but found the line strongly. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Leading player again. SUPER STORM (3) is a last start winner worth following up.",
